{"tid":1654677,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［全球反共系列］《長毛雪寶》現九段線　越南全線落畫","createTime":"2019-10-14T16:54:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T16:54:27.000Z","uid":262328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ee2a3707727c7a2dc6fb29faa38a5f41664398dc","tid":1654677,"uid":262328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T16:54:27.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】一齣由中美兩地聯手製作的動畫電影，由於其中一幕地圖上出現南海「九段線」，越南當局下令電影落畫。<br />\n<br />\n引發問題的是《長毛雪寶》這一幕，角色身後一幅顯示南海的地圖畫有「九段線」，即中國主張擁有南海主權的範圍界線。<br />\n<br />\n動畫電影由東方夢工廠和美國夢工場聯合製作，10月4日在越南首映，這一幕的圖片於網上廣傳後越南政府不滿，註銷電影牌照，電影在周日全線戲院落畫。<br />\n<br />\n南海主權爭議涉及多國，越南是其中之一，越南一直不承認中國的九段線，認為違反國際海洋公約，侵犯越南領土主權。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=366247&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D366247%26refer%3D&d=ZEuQNtRgUz7rCGSUvjEm92yAt0yGCUsyxQooKadsmXE%3D&h=c49a9d0d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D366247%26refer%3D&h=961dbaad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=366247&amp;refer=</a>"}]}